title: DDFP 425: Pro Bowl Preview & Everything else that matters
itunes:title: DDFP 425: Pro Bowl Preview & Everything else that matters
description:
Shek sits down with Maurice Jones-Drew, Ike Taylor, and the Sklar Brothers to preview Super Bowl 50 and the Pro Bowl. The guys talk about Denver Broncos uniform decision, as well as the age difference between Peyton Manning and Cam Newton. Lastly the Sklar brothers talk about the Los Angeles Rams, and how they will approach the new team. Will Peyton Manning be able to compete with the Panthers? Why are the Broncos wearing white? Will Shek ever ask "what's the poop" again? Find out more on DDFP.
